name: starwars_xx trading card #21: Kylolet
description:
Obviously this is Kylo during a particularly rebellious phase.
 
The more harmless kind of rebellion than what he would get up to later in life, seeking refuge in some kind of vaporwave landscape from all the suffocating pressure of expectations from his family. 

Kylo and his violet lightsaber in his little punky tartan skirt.
